Name: [Ally] Sumoboo
Desc:
All squad members' CRIT DMG increases by <color=#2BAD00>16%</color>.
Active Skill: Jumps towards the target and executes a downward strike, dealing <color=#F0D12B>Physical DMG</color> in an area. This skill is good at interrupting.
Desc2: Small but functional, it's a great help to Proxies in the Hollows.
